title: PPPP’s Nafeesa Shah wins NA-202 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Pakistan People’s Party Parliamentarian (PPPP) candidate Nafeesa Shah has won the election for National Assembly constituency NA-202 Khairpur-I by securing 1,46,083 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Grand Democratic Alliance (GDA) Syed Ghaus Ali Shah, who bagged 28,613 votes.
Overall voters’ turn-out remained 45.38 percent.
